snippet.textDisplay:
'Tajdar-e-haram' ताजदार-ए-हरम' is the title of Our Beloved Prophet Muhammad (Salallahu alaihi wasallam) Peace be upon him.
Tajdar means the winner and conqueror
Haram means the holy place Kaaba which is located in mecca, Saudi Arabia.
Tajdar-e-Haram means the conqueror of Kaaba (Muhammad SAW)
